{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_03_02",
  "title": "鈴村優 2話 誰のせいや思てるん",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――TRINITYAiLEクリスマスライブ、当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—On the day of TRINITYAiLE’s Christmas concert",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐライブだけど……調子はどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The concert’s about to start. How do you feel?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.1828797658
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん絶好調やわぁ\nきっちり仕上げてきたからなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re in excellent condition‚ of course‚\nbecause we got everything sorted out just right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ～今日はライブでファンのみんなと\n盛り上がったら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re going to get pumped up with all the fans\nat today’s show…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "そのままの勢いで三人でパーティーや～\nめっちゃ楽しみやなぁ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And carrying on that mood‚ the three of us will have our party.\nI’m so looking forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんのおかげで\n今日はうちの人生で一番のクリスマスです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to you‚ {user}‚\nthis is the best Christmas in my life.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.3
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そう言ってもらえると助かるよ。本当にすまなかった\n……おっと、そろそろだな。緊張感は忘れないでくれよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m so happy to hear you say so. I’m really sorry about before.\nOh‚ it’s nearly time. Don’t lose your edge.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "はい、最高のステージにしてみせます～\nそこは安心しとってやぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll make it the best show!\nDon’t worry about that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "鈴村さんには無用の心配だったな。じゃあ\n天動さんと奥山さんの様子も見てくるから頼んだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess I was needlessly worried about you. See you later.\nI’m going to check in on Tendo and Okuyama‚ so I’ll leave the show to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、ちょっと待って、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait a minute‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃんには、パーティーのこと言わんといてな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t say anything about the party to Sumire‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why not?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、瑠依ちゃんとうちとで\n逆サプライズ仕掛けるつもりなんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui and I set up\na reverse surprise trick for her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "え？　奥山さんに話してないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? And you didn’t tell Okuyama?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう。ライブの後、これでクリスマスおしまいか～\nはあ～、残念、って思わせて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep. After the show‚ we’ll be like “so this is the end of Christmas…”\nso she’ll think it’s a downer‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "実は――って感じで驚かすつもりやねんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but actually‚ we’ll have a surprise for her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "ケーキも用意したし、プレゼントも買うてあるし\nすみれちゃん、めっちゃ喜んでくれるはずやわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We got a cake‚ and bought presents‚\nI’m sure Sumire will be really happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "なくなったはずのサプライズパーティーが\nサプライズ返しでまさかの復活！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The surprise party she thought we lost\nwill make a surprise comeback!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "……なんて知ったら、喜びも倍増やん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’ll be twice as happy‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、もともとは奥山さんがサプライズパーティーを\n準備してたんだったよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ it was Okuyama who was originally\npreparing the surprise party.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "随分手が込んでるんだな\n分かった。奥山さんには内緒にしておくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You put a lot into this.\nI understand. I won’t say anything to Okuyama.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます～\n……それから、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you.\nAnyway‚ {user}‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "今回はわがまま言うて、ごめんなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "sorry for being so demanding this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いいよ。鈴村さんは\nあえて悪役を引き受けたんだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s okay. You always take the role\nof being the difficult one‚ Yu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_02-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "――え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
